{
  "stem": "24346.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they used to count-- 5-4-- that anybody is missing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, like the SS men went through with the stick, counting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When it came to him, he said to the SS guard-- it was a higher rank-- [NON-ENGLISH]-- I want to tell you something that's very important.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the guy just took his number, and after he counted everybody, the count was fine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went back to the barracks-- prisoner number blah, blah, blah, please come out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Took him on the SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obviously, he told him, [NON-ENGLISH], I found in my uniform that got assigned gold, and I wanted some extra money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I gave it to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went to the kapo they had, and they gave me a little extra food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I haven't got no more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I gave him all I had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now they're beating me for no reason.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The SS man said nothing-- OK, got your story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Go back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, that head kapo takes him into his little office, there in our barrack, because he was separated-- didn't sleep with us, had cut off for himself, like, a separate room.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened there?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave him a beating, and he told him",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told him, I had to tell him that this guy that gave him the gold, and he gave it to you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As soon as he went out, they took him in the washroom where we washed every morning, cold water, put a two-by-four over his neck.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They stepped on it, and they killed him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So now, he can't blame it on them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, this young man that hit me, that guy from Vienna-- he was maybe 19, 20-- he must have committed a crime, because no Germans or Viennese, Austrians, were in camp for no reason.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
